{"tid":1349903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民間自衛術義教班，現已正式成立！","createTime":"2019-07-22T11:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T16:33:03.000Z","uid":58104,"like":152,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"a77104e2835ab06607618a52f317017deb7e61ba","tid":1349903,"uid":58104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"有見及現今香港出現大量黑社會暴徒襲擊民眾，然警隊公開表示其不夠人手維持治安，本人現號召市民成立民間自衛隊，並開始身體力行設立民間自衛術義教班，目的教會市民正確防守姿勢，期望各位能保護好自己為首要目標。<br />\n<br />\n現招募：<br />\n文書(協助整理文宣及宣傳)<br />\n管理(各區負責人，包括負責臨時場地租用/及後有資金負責各區租用固定場地)<br />\n義教(只需教基本防禦動作)<br />\n學員(歡迎任何人，藍絲除外)<br />\n物資(訓練裝備)<br />\n資金(長期/臨時租用場地)<br />\n<br />\ntg公海：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/GDu-8lldrpGlfxVTJPIUkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FGDu-8lldrpGlfxVTJPIUkg&d=xXKwZA8amEcq1HGFygGyKj2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=2e0a3ddb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/GDu-8lldrpGlfxVTJPIUkg</a><br />\n<br />\nps<br />\n公海一定有鬼 <br />\n但有存在既必要<br />\n人口基數先係成事關鍵<br />\n大家自己注意言論<br />\n出黎練習既朋友我地會互相認識<br />\n認識後會開private tg gp再傾下可以再進一步為社會做d咩"},{"pid":"d9a035f753703b1ed216a323c01d9db9d7b6621c","tid":1349903,"uid":131352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:27:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43ea36419a0b680105230ea75b5ba50d3122381c","tid":1349903,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:28:08.000Z","msg":"何君堯中環皇后大道中5號衡怡大廈18樓律師樓好太平<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1349881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1349881</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a1db1c9307b0a632fe180fc83b4443b13034e708","tid":1349903,"uid":231594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:28:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8e1e4af06ad16f6e7576a371a6f7368ed463ae48","tid":1349903,"uid":36091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T11:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"